=== Detailed Description ===
this feature have two modes: mirror and redirect
mirror mode is the ability to send all VMs traffic of a specific network to a single VM
redirect is the ability to redirect all the traffic of VMs in a network to a single VM and it will decide to forward it or to a abort, common use case is a Firewall.

